&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has become available to work as a Band 5 Registered Nurse within the surgical wards at Eastbourne DGH.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The division has 3 surgical wards which takes elective patients across many surgical specialities and emergency patients for Urology and ENT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and well-motivated Staff Nurses to join our busy teams. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will need to have an interest in surgical nursing and relevant experience , but it is just as important that you have the right attitude towards learning, team work and delivery of care. We welcome applications from newly qualified nurses.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We will provide a supportive atmosphere, mentorship and clinical supervision and are committed to professional development of all staff.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Our aim is to provide the highest quality patient care in a safe and happy working environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tracey Dougan  Matron&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 03001314500 ext 36648 or 136661&lt;/p&gt;
